    <thetext>Description of problem:


Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): gtk3 3.20.5


How reproducible: select any jpg image on a web site and &quot;save As&quot;


Steps to Reproduce:
1. Select a jpg image on a web page 
2. Save As

Actual results: The image is saved but firefox crashes


Expected results: The image is saved and firefox continues normally


Additional info:

The problem doesn&apos;t occur if the image file is a png file.

Problem can be resolved by downgrading gtk3 3.20.5 to gtk3 3.20.4.</thetext>
